<sentence id="6">However , all 20 cases lacked the t(15 ; 17 ) and 17 cases tested <scope type="neg" id="3"><cue type="neg" id="3">lacked</cue> the promyelocytic/retinoic acid receptor alpha ( RAR alpha ) fusion transcript in RT-PCR assays ; 12 cases had 46 , XX or 46 , XY karyotypes</scope> , whereas 2 cases had abnormalities of chromosome 17q : 1 with del(17)(q25) and the other with t(11 ; 17 ) ( q23 ; q21 ) and the promyelocytic leukemia zinc finger/RAR alpha fusion transcript .</sentence>
