<sentence id="8">Four of 6 cases tested showed functional NK cell-mediated cytotoxicity , <scope type="spec" id="8"> <cue type="spec" id="8">suggesting</cue> a relationship between these unique CD33+ , CD56+ , CD16- acute leukemias and normal CD56+ , CD16- NK precursor cells</scope> .</sentence>
<sentence id="9">Using a combination of panning and multiparameter flow cytometric sorting , we identified a normal CD56+ , CD33+ , CD16- counterpart cell at a frequency of 1 % to 2 % in the peripheral blood of healthy individuals .</sentence>
